{"tid":234352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大義滅親片】女同學借宿被性侵   阿仔報警捉淫父","createTime":"2017-05-08T08:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T05:04:36.000Z","uid":48093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"902b21cc8a6d0e25b2739773915d05408b203c17","tid":234352,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170508/large/1494226200_cbd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170508%2Flarge%2F1494226200_cbd2.jpg&h=795c61f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣桃園一名高中女生小綠（化名）前晚到友人家借宿一宵，沒想到昨日凌晨友人的父親強行入房性侵小綠。友人十分懊悔，來不及營救，小綠向他哭訴遭到其父性侵。警方錄取口供後，依涉嫌觸犯妨害性自主罪將疑犯移送偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n受害的高中女生小綠因家庭因素，前晚借住同樣就讀高中的友人家中。友人家裏除父母，還有兩名年幼弟弟，一家5口共處一室。因小綠第一次借宿，友人體恤並釋出善意，特地騰出自己房間，讓她與6歲的弟弟一起睡，自己則與7個月大的弟弟屈就隔壁倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n不料，昨日清晨友人的母親起床，發現小綠睡的房間外竟擺放着自己丈夫的鞋子，房門還反鎖、十分詭異。友人被媽媽叫醒後，趕緊打電話，但小綠卻遲遲沒有接聽，他更加心急，不斷敲門。但父親不願開門，接着就聽見房內傳出哭泣的聲音。友人因為十分擔心小綠的安危，不斷用力踹門，父親才十分不悅地開門，進入房內發現小綠蜷曲床上，全身顫抖、哭哭啼啼。<br />\n<br />\n友人即場質問父親有沒有欺負小綠，父親堅決否認，但小綠則是淚流滿面，哭訴遭到性侵。友人不得已只能大義滅親，報警抓狼父。警方偵訊時，友人父親仍矢口否認犯案。友人則痛批：「非常不恥父親的行徑。」"},{"pid":"729d63da967f853be08b2a53b7f61e70009435d9","tid":234352,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"寶島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞自己新抱"},{"pid":"a2c9d440caceb75ccdb6702e7956e842d67a8f09","tid":234352,"uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"仔:我都未屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b932d315a6d54ade8862c67105e795f30cd6ce7b","tid":234352,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"友人十分懊悔，來不及營救"},{"pid":"43d52e0afdd01e23f6f0018bc9511da091861120","tid":234352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10e70ce7413fa16bdafa296d2ecd4df50548ab8","tid":234352,"uid":22259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"桃園+1"},{"pid":"eb02dd786db4aa6d3d3fc0f32149d4e2c4d8b45f","tid":234352,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"六歲弟弟去咗邊"},{"pid":"7dff944f1c0172f9ef78e2f158820b4355622ac4","tid":234352,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的xx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e54870088d5b109e13fa7e366abd2c98108e3d","tid":234352,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"台灣人個腦同畜生無分別<br />\n就係識做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b5f4ee5d6170e647b57816d293c5be4b22712b","tid":234352,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"友人體恤並釋出善意 <br />\n咩黎"},{"pid":"36cf3024b48fdc4dcde01476f6d7017e6ffa3b86","tid":234352,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>友人體恤並釋出善意 <br />\n咩黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：中途出家：釋出善意論<br />\n<br />\n以前讀過化學，知道甚麼是釋出。燃燒硫磺，釋出二氧化硫；投擲臭蛋在地，釋出硫化氫等臭氣。臭屎一桶，於舊日的農戶而言，是充滿善意的，屎愈臭愈能夠肥田，但農戶也要密密蓋住，就怕它在不適當的時候，釋出善意。<br />\n人對人的善意，政府對人民的善意，又不是臭屎，理應大方顯示，愈早顯示愈好，友誼愈綿長，社會愈和諧。然而，語言癌腫是會上腦的。即使到了違背原意、自我嘲諷的地步，習慣了程式中文和工程語言的人，也會照講如儀。近日的例子是北京向香港民主黨的政制改良方案忽然開綠燈，「釋出善意」，令民建聯等建制派人士錯愕非常，無法調整身段。善意與好意，如果已在心中，應說是「示好」、「顯示善意」、「伸出友誼之手」，怎會小心翼翼收藏，鬼鬼祟祟釋出，將一眾支持者殺個措手不及的呢？"},{"pid":"7192a8b8c14e1fd1ad1c9d1d7894757c6bd01fd6","tid":234352,"uid":50708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"老豆：死衰仔借條女比老豆屌下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2f9d64c7ab088838b98cdb3a71ac292dc90a9a","tid":234352,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"桃園GO!"},{"pid":"325cf7adb6beb2bc385a7537a1b34257a7c8bcda","tid":234352,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bad3705f23d1adc74cd6a26b5b2c06a6cff6a7b8","tid":234352,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 益下老豆都唔得"},{"pid":"473c0b312a8ec68b55eb334cc0f3b2a45505b195","tid":234352,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9954be9f5fd2cca5a8e13cb35c1cdc148c5dc7f","tid":234352,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"阿仔：我都未屌過<br />\n你屌左先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ee36832511c50ab67f3667f0fea089c7873c35","tid":234352,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"揚撚左佢老豆都繼續姦係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6ba1d69e8b459a39b06274461abe8c19d13864","tid":234352,"uid":38959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揚撚左佢老豆都繼續姦係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正宗一不做二不休<br />\n屌左先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9573d2d2df764624c5a782a86599868784731d7","tid":234352,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"桃園得一分"},{"pid":"ac2bce48c360ee70612437a20877aa348325ebd5","tid":234352,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0